profile:
Overhead Door of Nova Scotia is a garage door specialist for residential, commercial, agricultural and industrial applications, proudly serving the Nova Scotia area. We would love for you to visit our showroom at 101-420 Higney Ave, Dartmouth. There, our team can give you personalized advice in purchasing a garage door, an installation that meets the highest industry standards, and unequalled after-sales service thanks to our maintenance and repair program.

Our full range of products also includes electric garage door openers as well as many other accessories to go with your garage door. Think of us when it comes to buying, installing or repairing any type of garage door.

Our showroom is located at 101-420 Higney Ave, Dartmouth and is open Monday to Friday from 8 AM to 4:30 PM.

I invite you to come and visit us, and on behalf of our entire team, I thank you for considering our company.

Dave Pace
Owner
Overhead Door of Nova Scotia
